Package: ArgentinAPI
Type: Package
Title: Access Argentine Economic, Social, and Geopolitical Data via RESTful APIs and Curated Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Renzo Caceres Rossi <arenzocaceresrossi@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions to access data from the 'ArgentinaDatos API' and the 'REST Countries API'
    related to Argentina's exchange rates, inflation, political figures, holidays, and general
    country-level indicators. Additionally, the package includes curated datasets related to Argentina,
    covering topics such as economic indicators, biodiversity, agriculture, human rights, genetic data,
    and consumer prices. The package supports research and analysis focused on Argentina by integrating
    open APIs with high-quality datasets from various domains. For more details on the 'ArgentinaDatos API',
    see <https://argentinadatos.com/> and for 'REST Countries', see <https://restcountries.com/>.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/lightbluetitan/argentinapi, https://lightbluetitan.github.io/argentinapi/
BugReports: https://github.com/lightbluetitan/argentinapi/issues
